      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING ZEPPELIN (8) produced an impressive 29.49 to claim a Grade 4/5 over 520m at this track last start. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. VALLEY CASH (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (17.79) from Box 2 at Richmond Straight. Boasts a strong record from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from seven starts. Hard to beat again. RECLUSE (4) finished third (30.04) two back at Wentworth Park but out of the placings last time when 7th there. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from three starts. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Expected to feature in the finish. ZIPPING BALBOA (5) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
